{"tid":44164,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺昅靚女同昅靚仔嘅標準爭好遠?","createTime":"2016-12-18T05:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T06:48:29.000Z","uid":25781,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41706516195d57c361ea3753024460f3900a2052","tid":44164,"uid":25781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"喺香港，基本上求其喺街指一個女仔出嚟都可以短時間內塑造成為靚女/女神。<br />\n先講外表，你只需要係大眾樣，基本上都可以靠化妝補救。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高度就唔駛講啦，150矮妹去到175高妹都總有佢嘅市場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身材就仲簡單，喺港女都係無波嘅情況下，好自然就會睇腳。我敢講只要唔係象腿同美極，出到街一定有男人偷望。最起碼你睇吓啲呀叔嘅眼神。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁男嘅又點呢?<br />\n外表喇喎，唔到中上樣都唔駛旨意有人覺得靚仔啦。你睇吓正常樣就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高度方面，175先叫正常人。唔過170仲會俾人笑矮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以起碼都180先會比人覺得與別不同啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到身材 ，瘦嘅唔駛講:除非你夠高，唔係會俾人笑瘦撚，唔夠man。所以點都要練大隻先會俾人昅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b5350a8365047be188637978a120fc13cefcf4","tid":44164,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"837905b188104ca57cb84979adbecbdddead78f3","tid":44164,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:30:21.000Z","msg":"黎做乜？<br />\n好需要被關注？"},{"pid":"f57176ef2289264d3d66162ce31be2dfb005f52b","tid":44164,"uid":53895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:59:27.000Z","msg":"地方毒撚需要愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcba53c6191a4cd34226c2f3370b9cfb6733927","tid":44164,"uid":31545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"結論:樓豬175"}]}